        "title": "fix(release): gate beta publish on plugin verification",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- gate `openclaw-release-publish.yml` so the GitHub release page is created and proof is appended only after postpublish verification succeeds\n- fail early when a public release already exists for the tag without verification evidence for the current target SHA\n- temporarily make `llama-cpp` source-checkout-only by removing npm/ClawHub publish/install/catalog/docs surfaces until the first package publish is prepared\n- update release maintainer instructions to preflight newly publishable plugin packages before tagging/publishing\n\n## Verification\n\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/commands/doctor-memory-search.test.ts extensions/memory-core/src/memory/embeddings.test.ts extensions/llama-cpp/index.test.ts test/scripts/release-beta-verifier.test.ts test/scripts/package-acceptance-workflow.test.ts src/plugins/bundled-plugin-naming.test.ts src/plugins/official-external-plugin-catalog.test.ts test/plugin-npm-release.test.ts test/plugin-clawhub-release.test.ts test/scripts/list-prod-store-packages.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/generate-plugin-inventory-doc.mjs --check`\n- `node scripts/docs-list.js`\n- `ruby -e 'require \"yaml\"; YAML.load_file(\".github/workflows/openclaw-release-publish.yml\"); puts \"workflow yaml ok\"'`\n- `node -e 'JSON.parse(require(\"fs\").readFileSync(\"docs/docs.json\",\"utf8\")); console.log(\"docs json ok\")'`\n- `git diff --check`\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode branch --base origin/release/2026.6.6`\n- `node scripts/crabbox-wrapper.mjs run -provider azure -class Standard_D4ads_v6 -- env OPENCLAW_CHECK_CHANGED_REMOTE_CHILD=1 OPENCLAW_CHANGED_LANES_RAW_SYNC=1 corepack pnpm check:changed` (`cbx_bb90342a999f`, `jade-crayfish`)\n\n## Notes\n\n- `@openclaw/llama-cpp-provider` is not present on npm yet; this PR hides public install instructions rather than telling users to install a 404.\n- Local npm dist-tag promotion is still blocked on this machine because npm auth and 1Password are not signed in.\n",
